quote.p:
Notes with gratification that the UNRep has reported that the Govts of India
and Pak have accepted all but two of the
paras of his twelve point proposals;

Records its gratitude to the UNRep for India and Pak for the great efforts which he has made to achieve a
settlement and requests him to continue to make his services available to
the Govts of India and Pak to this end;
